{"type": "game", "name": "Schachkampf - Fantasy Chess", "steam_appid": 1945700, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Over 3.000.000 chess puzzles -</h2>One playthrough of a map contains 54 different chess puzzles which differ in difficulty from mate in 1 to mate in 4. But every time you start a new run, you get 54 new puzzles out of the big pool of 3.000.000 puzzles.<br><img src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1945700/extras/Banner_Puzzles.gif?t=1704265669\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Scalable AI -</h2>Schachkampf uses stockfish AI and you can choose between 100 levels of difficulty. On level 1 even an absolute beginner can get a win, but on level 100 not even a pro player could beat the game.<br><img src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1945700/extras/Banner_AI.gif?t=1704265669\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- 12 different boards to play on -</h2>You have 12 handcrafted boards to unlock and play on, all in the style of 90s JRPGs. The levels differ from cozy woods or small towns up to icy woods.<br><img src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1945700/extras/Banner_Boards.gif?t=1704265669\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Local multiplayer -</h2>If you have friends in real life you can play against them locally. If you don\u2019t, you can still play with remote connect against your virtual friends.<br><img src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1945700/extras/Banner_LocalMultiplayer.png?t=1704265669\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- 12 different starting variations -</h2>If you want some extra challenge you can unlock up to 12 different starting variations for your chess game. Each of them will lead to different strategies and tactics.<br><img src=\"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1945700/extras/Banner_Variants.gif?t=1704265669\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">- Play in classic chess view or in a sideways view -</h2>You can choose in which direction the pieces can move. If you hav